Start 
  Play button
    Creates and shuffles the deck
      Stack for deck
      Stack for trash
      Shuffle fuction on deck stack
    Creates the peaks
      Consider peaks as Four arrays
        Bottom, LowerMid, UpperMid, Top
        Assign lengths independently
    Populates peaks
      Take from the deck stack and deal to each array
    Burns one card to trash pile
    Rest sit in deck stack
    
  In play
    Click function
      On card in peak
        Tests if playable
          If playable, plays
            Check on same array index, and index +1
          If not, does nothing
      On deck
        Adds card to trash pile
        Becomes active card
    
